title: So, which ‘Friends’ character did Jane Krakowski auditioned for?
text:
Other Articles Don't sit! Targeting exercise doesn't reduce effects of prolonged sitting Exes Freida Pinto, Dev Patel reunite for charity Ryan Reynolds caught close pal 'red-handed' selling his daughter's photos Jane Krakowski just revealed a big secret at the 2015 Emmy Awards on Sunday as she said that she auditioned for ‘Friends.’
The 46-year-old actress said like almost every actor in the world she auditioned for the hit series, reports Us magazine.
The actress, who wore a Bibhu Mohapatra gown, added that she wishes she would have got that role and revealed that she auditioned for the role of Rachel.
Krakowski further joked that her business manager was very sad that she didn’t get the part.
 21, 2015 12:28 pm
